overview: PrioCom is a leading Ukrainian system integrator of professional solutions for telecom operators and large enterprises. PrioCom provide full-cycle services for an enterprise IT infrastructer including networks, cloud DataCenters, VPN, unified communications and others. PrioCom designs and implements also telecom solutions for all sectors of the operator activity, from infrastructure to business applications.
